<h2 class="bold font-l">BB - Family Conference</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In Season 5 &quot;Hawk and Chick&quot;, the Belchers have a family huddle when Louise comes up with an idea to reunite Koji and Yukki together and Koji sneaks in the huddle. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="gq6gxa" data-video-descrip="The Riveras huddle up backstage at the Sunrise Spectacular to go over their plan." data-video-title="Coco" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/gq6gxa_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/gq6gxa.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/HuddleShot" data-video-tropename="Huddle Shot" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/Coco" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/gq6gxa.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Coco</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="aeio1l" data-video-descrip="When Mojo Jojo inflitrates the girls' slumber party in disguise, the girls get in a huddle to talk." data-video-title="The Powerpuff Girls" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/aeio1l_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/aeio1l.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/HuddleShot" data-video-tropename="Huddle Shot" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/ThePowerpuffGirls" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/aeio1l.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">The Powerpuff G...</span></p>
</a>
</div>
